<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="104" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,675,882]" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,267,675,701]" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Burmeister" baseAuthorityYear="1865" box="[276,575,675,701]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Bisaltes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="adustus" subGenus="Bisaltes">
<emphasis box="[276,365,675,701]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">Bisaltes</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[382,471,675,701]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">Bisaltes</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[489,575,675,701]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">adustus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see photographs on 
<bibRefCitation author="Bezark, L. G." box="[821,979,675,701]" pageId="9" pageNumber="104" refId="ref4337" refString="Bezark, L. G. (2022 a) A photographic Catalog of the Cerambycidae of the World. New World Cerambycidae Catalog. Available from: http: // bezbycids. com / byciddb / wdefault. asp? w = n / (accessed 22 April 2022.)" type="url" year="2022">Bezark 2022a</bibRefCitation>
) was described based on a single specimen from 
<collectingCountry box="[271,382,711,737]" name="Argentina" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">Argentina</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[400,512,711,737]" country="Argentina" name="Tucuman" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">Tucumán</collectingRegion>
). 
<bibRefCitation author="Monne, M. A." box="[532,696,711,737]" pageId="9" pageNumber="104" refId="ref5080" refString="Monne, M. A. (2022) Catalogue of the Cerambycidae (Coleoptera) of the Neotropical region. Part II. Subfamily Lamiinae. Available from: https: // cerambycids. com / catalog / (accessed 22 April 2022.)" type="url" year="2022">Monné (2022)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Tavakilian, G. L. &amp; Chevillotte, H." box="[754,1121,711,737]" pageId="9" pageNumber="104" refId="ref5126" refString="Tavakilian, G. L. &amp; Chevillotte, H. (2021) Titan: base de donnees internationales sur les Cerambycidae ou Longicornes. Available from: http: // titan. gbif. fr / (accessed 23 April 2022.)" type="url" year="2021">Tavakilian &amp; Chevillotte (2021)</bibRefCitation>
report that the species was described based on 
<typeStatus box="[376,478,748,774]" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">syntypes</typeStatus>
. However, there is no evidence of this in the original description. 
<bibRefCitation author="Breuning, S." box="[1235,1436,747,773]" pageId="9" pageNumber="104" pagination="285 - 288" refId="ref4726" refString="Breuning, S. (1971 b) Neue Lamiinae aus den Bestanden des Zoologischen Museums der Humboldt-Universitat in Berlin (Col., Cerambycidae). Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum in Berlin, 47 (2), 285 - 288. https: // doi. org / 10.1002 / mmnz. 19710470206" type="journal article" year="1971">Breuning (1971b)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName box="[267,449,784,809]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Bisaltes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="argentinensis">
<emphasis box="[267,449,784,809]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">B. argentinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see photograph on 
<bibRefCitation author="Bezark, L. G." box="[683,841,783,809]" pageId="9" pageNumber="104" refId="ref4337" refString="Bezark, L. G. (2022 a) A photographic Catalog of the Cerambycidae of the World. New World Cerambycidae Catalog. Available from: http: // bezbycids. com / byciddb / wdefault. asp? w = n / (accessed 22 April 2022.)" type="url" year="2022">Bezark 2022a</bibRefCitation>
) from 
<collectingCountry box="[918,1029,783,809]" name="Argentina" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">Argentina</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[1046,1108,783,809]" country="Argentina" name="Salta" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">Salta</collectingRegion>
). Comparing the original descriptions, specimens of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Burmeister" baseAuthorityYear="1865" box="[434,604,819,845]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Bisaltes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="adustus" subGenus="Bisaltes">
<emphasis box="[434,458,820,845]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">B.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[476,500,820,845]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">B.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[518,604,819,845]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">adustus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and a photograph of the 
<typeStatus box="[902,1000,819,845]" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName box="[1041,1223,820,845]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Bisaltes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="argentinensis">
<emphasis box="[1041,1223,820,845]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">B. argentinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, we did not find a reliable difference. Therefore, 
<taxonomicName box="[493,724,855,881]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Bisaltes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="argentinensis" subGenus="Bisaltes">
<emphasis box="[493,517,856,881]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">B.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[533,558,856,881]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">B.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[574,724,856,881]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">argentinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is synonymized with 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Burmeister" baseAuthorityYear="1865" box="[969,1136,855,881]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Bisaltes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="adustus" subGenus="Bisaltes">
<emphasis box="[969,994,856,881]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">B.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[1010,1034,856,881]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">B.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[1050,1136,855,881]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="104">adustus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
